<p>And Chris admits he has never really 'dealt' with his childhood trauma.</p>

<p>Speaking to The Hollywood Reporter, he added: 'I'm not belittling today's youth, but I wish somebody had sent me a bad text when I was a kid. These m************ were trying to kill me ... </p>

<p>'I thought I was actually dealing with it, and the reality is I never dealt with it. </p>

<p>'The reality was the pain and the fear that brought me, I was experiencing it every day.'</p>

