<p>Chris has also been learning to swim during lockdown.</p>

<p>He shared: 'Do you know how f****** hard it is for a grown-up to learn how to swim? You've got to not be scared to die. </p>

<p>'The other day, this guy says to me, 'OK, you're going to dive into the deep end and swim to the other side,' and I'm like, 'Are you f****** crazy?</p>

<p>' But then I dove into the deep end and I swam to the other side, and it's a metaphor for what I've been trying to do during this time.'</p>
